\
11. President Barack Obama signed the Affordable Care Act expanding health coverage and protections (2010-03-23): Enacting the ACA broadened access to healthcare and created durable entitlements, strengthening the social safety net that later executive actions can either erode or build upon.\
\
12. President Donald Trump issued an executive order requiring documentary proof of citizenship for federal voter registration and tightening ballot deadlines (2025-03-25): Mandating documentary proof of citizenship and restricting mail ballot counting by executive order reconfigures election access nationwide from the White House, risking large-scale disenfranchisement and legal clashes with states and Congress.\
